Needlenose, following behind Slugslinger, began to feel weak.  As he 
lost energy he began to float in towards the Hidden One , finally 
knocking into the side.  

Havotron finally gave the order.  "Fire on the ship. Take it out of 
the sky. "  But all of a sudden they were in the field.  Havotron 
slumped into his chair as he was weakended.  "What is this..."  Q

Quake fell out of his chair.  "Ugggg....""
